{"tid":1517783,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(三毛) 國歌啟發咗我","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T06:29:16.000Z","uid":79882,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9135f3cdd910467d88c71cc14f40a0252b59f16b","tid":1517783,"uid":79882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:32:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的。<br />\n國歌由細聽到大，裏面嘅歌詞刻骨銘心。<br />\n因為聽到<span style=\"color: red;\">起來不願做奴隸的人們</span>，唔再安於現狀俾人劏。<br />\n因為聽到<span style=\"color: red;\">到了最危險的時候每個人都發出最後的哮聲</span>，到咗送中法就企出嚟。<br />\n因為聽到<span style=\"color: red;\">築成新的長城</span>，我去咗前幾日人鏈。<br />\n因為聽到<span style=\"color: red;\">冒著敵人的炮火前進</span>所以我出去發夢。<br />\n多謝國歌教我受壓迫要企出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdac798d0a00dcab598f7c36290c4cc01a71cae","tid":1517783,"uid":60685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3325bf2c66638eea8b421a597d66eca676abdf7e","tid":1517783,"uid":79882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:32:52.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"999d594a54e9ed2c0a8f0945e76890ce3ebe4426","tid":1517783,"uid":79882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:33:03.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"f89a216e6497d481add90e066ed5ac2b7eaa4785","tid":1517783,"uid":79882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"f6c534f82e090456f4e5a3b0d04f756d2f49d46d","tid":1517783,"uid":79882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:33:23.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"9f8ede4734783b6a7e26eaa20bffdfec636b36fb","tid":1517783,"uid":79882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"78f07316f29501f95d9b12f947701810f5378a5d","tid":1517783,"uid":79882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:33:47.000Z","msg"